data.description: Welcome to your solar powered dream home! This 5, possibly 6 Bedroom, 3 Bath stunning house is ''like new'' and ready for you to move in without the wait of construction. Offering a spacious floor plan and modern features, this home is a true gem. The property is not only aesthetically appealing but also environmentally conscious with its solar-powered system, generating about 1.4MWh of power each month eliminating your electric bill! Located in a secure, gated community, you'll enjoy a sense of safety and exclusive amenities that make this property even more appealing. Whether it's the community pool, tennis court, basketball court, fitness center, or clubhouse, you'll have plenty of options for recreation and relaxation right at your doorst This house combines the best of modern living, energy efficiency, and community amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this remarkable property your new home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the convenience and luxury for yourself.
